<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>최이 - 언어학 & 인지과학 연구자</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --accent: #3498db;
            --accent-light: #5dade2;
            --secondary: #7f8c8d;
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --bg-light: #f8f9fa;
            --border: #e0e0e0;
            --shadow: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            --timeline-bg: #ecf0f1;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--primary);
            background: var(--bg);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-light) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0 60px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><circle cx="50" cy="50" r="40" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.05)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .header-content h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .header-content .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .header-content .affiliation {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        nav a:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Sections */
        section {
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: var(--primary);
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
        }

        h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 60px;
            height: 4px;
            background: var(--accent);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        /* About */
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            align-items: start;
        }

        .about-text p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .quick-facts {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        }

        .quick-facts h3 {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .fact-item {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .fact-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .fact-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .keywords {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }

        .keyword {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .keyword:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Timeline Section */
        .timeline-container {
            position: relative;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .timeline-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        .timeline-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 80px 1fr;
            gap: 0;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:first-child {
            order: 3;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-marker {
            order: 2;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:last-child {
            order: 1;
        }

        .timeline-content {
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content:first-child {
            text-align: right;
            padding-right: 40px;
        }

        .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:last-child {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }

        .timeline-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow);
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px var(--shadow);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .timeline-marker {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .timeline-dot {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: white;
            border: 4px solid var(--accent);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--shadow);
        }

        .timeline-year {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .timeline-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .timeline-tag {
            padding: 4px 10px;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        /* Research */
        .research-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .research-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .research-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .research-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .research-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px var(--shadow);
            border-color: var(--accent);
        }

        .research-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .research-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .research-card p {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* Publications */
        .publication-list {
            display: grid;
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .publication {
            background: white;
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px var(--shadow);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .publication:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px var(--shadow);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .pub-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .pub-authors {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .pub-venue {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Projects */
        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 32px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 36px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px var(--shadow);
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px var(--shadow);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
        }

        .project-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .project-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .project-role {
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .project-desc {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .project-tags {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .tag {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            color: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* CV Download */
        .cv-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-light) 0%, white 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 2px dashed var(--border);
        }

        .cv-section p {
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.3);
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.4);
        }

        /* Contact */
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .contact-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px var(--shadow);
        }

        .contact-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .contact-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .contact-value {
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .contact-value a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .contact-value a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-light);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            color: var(--secondary);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header {
                padding: 60px 0 40px;
            }

            .header-content h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .about-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }

            .timeline-item {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

            .timeline-line {
                left: 30px;
            }

            .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:first-child,
            .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content:last-child {
                order: initial;
            }

            .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-marker {
                order: initial;
            }

            .timeline-content {
                padding-left: 80px !important;
                text-align: left !important;
            }

            .timeline-marker {
                position: absolute;
                left: 0;
            }

            .research-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .contact-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <h1>최이</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">언어학 & 인지과학 연구자</p>
                <p class="affiliation">
                    한양대학교 독어독문학과 석사과정<br>
                    LBCLAB (Language, Brain, and Cognition Lab)
                </p>
                <nav>
                    <a href="#about">소개</a>
                    <a href="#journey">연혁</a>
                    <a href="#research">연구</a>
                    <a href="#publications">논문</a>
                    <a href="#projects">프로젝트</a>
                    <a href="blog.html">블로그</a>
                    <a href="#cv">이력서</a>
                    <a href="#contact">연락</a>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section id="about">
            <h2>소개</h2>
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>
                        한양대학교 LBCLAB (Language, Brain, and Cognition Lab)에서 남윤주 교수님 지도 하에 석사과정을 밟고 있습니다. 언어학, 인지신경과학, 그리고 계산적 방법론을 결합하여 뇌가 언어를 처리하는 메커니즘을 연구하고 있습니다.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        한국외국어대학교에서 언어공학을 전공하며 계산언어학과 자연어처리에 대한 전문성을 쌓았습니다. 현재는 신경언어학 강의 조교로 활동하며, 한방 언어 코퍼스 구축 프로젝트를 주도하고 있습니다.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        장기적으로는 EEG와 fMRI 방법론을 결합한 한국어 처리 메커니즘 연구로 박사과정을 진행하여, 언어 구조가 뇌에서 어떻게 표상되고 처리되는지 밝히는 데 기여하고자 합니다.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="keywords">
                        <span class="keyword">신경언어학</span>
                        <span class="keyword">심리언어학</span>
                        <span class="keyword">형태론 & 통사론</span>
                        <span class="keyword">인지신경과학</span>
                        <span class="keyword">자연어처리</span>
                        <span class="keyword">EEG/fMRI</span>
                        <span class="keyword">한국어 처리</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="quick-facts">
                    <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
                    <div class="fact-item">
                        <div class="fact-label">현재</div>
                        <div class="fact-value">석사과정 2년차</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fact-item">
                        <div class="fact-label">소속</div>
                        <div class="fact-value">LBCLAB</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fact-item">
                        <div class="fact-label">지도교수</div>
                        <div class="fact-value">남윤주 교수님</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fact-item">
                        <div class="fact-label">학부</div>
                        <div class="fact-value">언어공학 전공</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fact-item">
                        <div class="fact-label">관심분야</div>
                        <div class="fact-value">뇌-언어 상호작용</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="journey">
            <h2>나의 학술 여정</h2>
            <div class="timeline-container">
                <div class="timeline-line"></div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2017</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-marker">
                        <div class="timeline-dot">🎓</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-card">
                            <div class="timeline-title">한국외국어대학교 입학</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">
                                언어공학 전공 시작. 컴퓨터과학과 언어학의 교차점에서 자연어처리와 계산언어학의 기초를 다짐
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-tags">
                                <span class="timeline-tag">언어공학</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">NLP</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2018-2020</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-marker">
                        <div class="timeline-dot">💻</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-card">
                            <div class="timeline-title">계산언어학 심화</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">
                                형태소 분석, 구문 분석, 의미 분석 등 NLP 핵심 과정 이수. 한국어 파서 개발 및 코퍼스 분석 프로젝트 수행
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-tags">
                                <span class="timeline-tag">파싱</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">형태소분석</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">코퍼스언어학</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-marker">
                        <div class="timeline-dot">✈️</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-card">
                            <div class="timeline-title">학부 졸업 & 새로운 시작</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">
                                언어공학 학위 취득. 언어의 계산적 측면을 넘어 인지적·신경학적 기반을 탐구하고자 대학원 진학 결심
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-tags">
                                <span class="timeline-tag">학사학위</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">진로탐색</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-marker">
                        <div class="timeline-dot">🧠</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-card">
                            <div class="timeline-title">한양대학교 대학원 입학</div>
                            <div class="timeline-desc">
                                독어독문학과 석사과정 시작. LBCLAB 합류하여 신경언어학 및 뇌인지과학 연구 본격화
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-tags">
                                <span class="timeline-tag">대학원</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">LBCLAB</span>
                                <span class="timeline-tag">신경언어학</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-year">2024</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-marker">
                        <div class="timeline-dot">📊</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-content">
                        <div class="timeline-card">
